description:
You are preparing a Tor Browser profile for an Intelligence Analyst. To streamline their Open Source Intelligence (OSINT) workspace and prevent accidental clicks, you must deeply customize the Tor Browser user interface using legacy userChrome.css features. Enable the 'toolkit.legacyUserProfileCustomizations.stylesheets' preference and create a 'userChrome.css' file within a 'chrome' directory in the browser's profile directory. The file must contain the following CSS content:

/* OSINT UI Hardening */
#tabs-newtab-button {
    display: none !important;
}
#unified-extensions-button {
    display: none !important;
}
.tab-background[selected="true"] {
    background-color: #ffaa00 !important;
}
